Third-Party Data Attribution
=============================

The cell-role classifier (src/sheet_call_tree/cell_classifier.joblib) was
trained using the following datasets:

1. ENTRANT
   Authors: Zavitsanos, E., Mavroeidis, D., Spyropoulou, E., Fergadiotis, M.,
            & Paliouras, G.
   Paper:   "ENTRANT: A Large Financial Dataset for Table Understanding"
            Sci Data 11, 876 (2024). https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-024-03605-5
   Data:    https://zenodo.org/records/10667088
   License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0)
   Subsets used: 18-K, 10-KT, 485BPOS, 497, S-1

2. CTC (CIUS & SAUS)
   Author:  Majid Ghasemi Gol
   Paper:   "Tabular Cell Classification Using Pre-Trained Cell Embeddings"
            (ICDM 2019)
   Source:  https://github.com/majidghgol/TabularCellTypeClassification
   License: MIT
   Subsets used: CIUS (train), SAUS (eval)

Per the CC-BY-4.0 and MIT license terms, this trained model constitutes
adapted material derived from the above datasets.
